		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Krebs on Security is running a <a href="http://krebsonsecurity.com/2010/11/captchabot-blurring-human-and-machine/" class="postlink">story about captchabot.com</a>, the CAPTCHA-solving service used by one of the biggest spambotnets.

		

